HEADWORD: Lycoperdales
<hw>Lycoperdales</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A small order of
basidiomycetous fungi having fleshy often globose fruiting bodies:
puffpalls; earthstars.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> order <ord>Lycoperdales</ord>.</syn>⟦br⟧
